<!--
  CHARGEN CUSTOM CONTENT SNIPPET

  Adds the Secret and Goal form fields to the chargen process.

  FILE: ares-webportal/app/components/chargen-custom.hbs

  This file outputs ONLY the <div class="tab-pane"> element for the custom
  chargen fields. It gets injected into the main chargen tab-content container.

  INSTALLATION:

  1. Open your game's ares-webportal/app/components/chargen-custom.hbs
  2. Copy the code block below this comment and paste it into your file:
     - If the file is empty, paste it as-is
     - If the file already has other tab-pane divs, add it after the closing </div>
       of another tab-pane entry

  IMPORTANT DETAILS:

  FILE STRUCTURE:
  - This file contains ONLY the <div class="tab-pane"> element, no wrapper tab-content
  - It gets inserted into the main chargen tab-content container
  - If you have other custom tabs from other plugins, add their <div class="tab-pane"> here too

  STRUCTURE:
  - The form has sections for Secret and Goal, each with a title field and
    description textarea
  - An <hr> divides the two sections
  - Bootstrap 5 classes (d-flex, form-label, form-control) style the fields

  ACTIVE CLASS:
  - The tab-pane has classes "fade active show" so it displays on page load.
  - If you want it to NOT be the active tab on load, remove "active show".

  ID MATCHING:
  - id="chargen-inklings-pane" MUST match the href in chargen-custom-tabs.snippet.hbs.
  - Do NOT change this value.

  FIELD NAMES:
  - inkling_secret_title, inkling_secret_text, inkling_goal_title, inkling_goal_text
  - These MUST match exactly what chargen-custom.snippet.js sends and what
    custom_char_fields.rb reads/writes. The chargen types are fixed to secret and
    goal - see README "Chargen Integration".
-->

<div class="tab-pane fade active show" id="chargen-inklings-pane">
  <div class="cg-tip">
    Add a secret and goal for your character. A secret is something that only your character knows and should be personal. A goal is something your character is working towards and should be actionable.
  </div>

  <section class="mb-4">
    <h2>Secret</h2>
    <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-2 mb-3" style="width: 98%;">
      <label for="chargen-secret-title" class="form-label mb-0">Title</label>
      {{input id="chargen-secret-title" type="text" class="form-control" value=this.char.custom.inkling_secret_title placeholder="A short name for your secret"}}
    </div>
    {{textarea id="chargen-secret-text" class="form-control" value=this.char.custom.inkling_secret_text rows=5 placeholder="Write a secret your character is hiding here. What don't they want others to know?"}}
  </section>

  <hr class="my-4">

  <section class="mt-4">
    <h2>Goal</h2>
    <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-2 mb-3" style="width: 98%;">
      <label for="chargen-goal-title" class="form-label mb-0">Title</label>
      {{input id="chargen-goal-title" type="text" class="form-control" value=this.char.custom.inkling_goal_title placeholder="A short name for your goal"}}
    </div>
    {{textarea id="chargen-goal-text" class="form-control" value=this.char.custom.inkling_goal_text rows=5 placeholder="Write a goal your character is working toward here. What do they want to achieve?"}}
  </section>
</div>
